title: We Couldn't Survive Our Teenage Years Without... | Ear Biscuits Ep. 340
description:
What do ramen, video games, and fan-fiction have in common? They’re all things you couldn’t survive without! Plus - How do you eat Hamburger Helper out of a Thermos? And Are Rhett and Link too old for video games?
On this episode, Rhett and Link react to your voicemail responses to "I could not have survived my teenage years without ______.” and talk about how their needs have changed over the years.
Want to hear your voice on Ear Biscuits? Call 1-888-EAR-POD1 and we might just play your call on an upcoming episode!
